name: Rinoa Heartilly - Final Fantasy VIII
description:
Rinoa Heartilly - Final Fantasy VIII

Here's a Rinoa Heartilly LoRA to compliment the Squall LoRA I made.

As with Squall, I was limited by the not-quite-realistic images that are available for Rinoa, so a photorealistic look may not be easy.
In V2, the best prompts to get a look close to her original look is 'rinoa, brown hair streaks, blue duster, blue wristbands'

Start with <lora:Rinoa:0.8> and adjust from there.

I trained the LoRA on her blue duster outfit, as well as her off-white dress from the ball. Good luck with the dress. It is VERY hard to get the halter straps, as it wants to render them as a necklace.

You can also try adding "finger point" and "hand on necklace" poses, but I've had mixed results with both.

modelVersions.description:

Much more defined hair streaks

Added "brown hair streaks" keywords
